rComments: Worst Prof. ever! Not at all approachable. Internet explains better than her. Rude, ridicules students.

Dr. Shin is an exemplary professor.  She went out of her way to create help sessions & office hrs to aid students.  I disagree with other comments made about her testing -- her tests are straight from the lecture material.  She's more concerned with us learning the material rather than tricking us with unforseeable test questions.  Fun course.
Not a good prof.  Doesn't test on knowledge, but basis marks randomly and on things not taught in class or text.  Also a mean person.  Makes rude comments and mocks students for asking questions.
